    zh:{'Shadow':'阴影','Tint':'浅色','Tone':'色调','Complement':'互补色','Split':'分裂互补色','Analogous':'类似色','Complementary':'互补色','Split Complementary':'分裂互补色','Triadic':'三角色','Tetradic':'四色','Square':'方形配色','White background':'白色背景','Black background':'黑色背景','contrast ratio on a white background':'白色背景上的对比度','contrast ratio on a black background':'黑色背景上的对比度','Protanopia':'红色盲','Deuteranopia':'绿色盲','Tritanopia':'蓝黄色盲','Achromatopsia':'全色盲','Open color picker':'打开取色器','Color history':'颜色历史','Copy foreground color':'复制前景色','Copy background color':'复制背景色','Copy color 1':'复制颜色 1','Copy color 2':'复制颜色 2','Converter pages':'转换页面','Tools pages':'工具页面','Names pages':'名称页面','Language':'语言','Split complementary':'分裂互补色','Shades of Black':'黑色系','Shades of Blue':'蓝色系','Shades of Brown':'棕色系','Shades of Gray':'灰色系','Shades of Green':'绿色系','Shades of Orange':'橙色系','Shades of Pink':'粉色系','Shades of Purple':'紫色系','Shades of Red':'红色系','Shades of White':'白色系','Shades of Yellow':'黄色系','Red HTML Color Names':'红色 HTML 颜色名称','Pink HTML Color Names':'粉色 HTML 颜色名称','Orange HTML Color Names':'橙色 HTML 颜色名称','Yellow HTML Color Names':'黄色 HTML 颜色名称','Purple HTML Color Names':'紫色 HTML 颜色名称','Green HTML Color Names':'绿色 HTML 颜色名称','Blue HTML Color Names':'蓝色 HTML 颜色名称','White HTML Color Names':'白色 HTML 颜色名称','Gray HTML Color Names':'灰色 HTML 颜色名称','Tailwind Color Chart':'Tailwind 颜色表','Flat Design Color Chart':'扁平设计颜色表','Material Design Color Chart':'Material Design 颜色表','Web Safe Color Chart':'网页安全颜色表','Tailwind CSS is a popular utility-first CSS framework that provides a wide range of pre-defined classes for styling HTML elements.':'Tailwind CSS 是流行的实用优先 CSS 框架，提供大量预定义类来为 HTML 元素设置样式。','Flat design or flat UI colors are quite popular in web design today where bold, bright colors are used to create clean, simple interfaces.':'扁平设计和扁平 UI 颜色在现代网页设计中很常见，常用大胆明亮的颜色创建简洁界面。','Material design is a visual language and design system developed by Google with an almost flat style and vibrant color schemes.':'Material Design 是 Google 推出的视觉语言和设计系统，具有近似扁平的风格和鲜明的配色。','Web safe colors emerged during the early era of the internet; a standardized palette of 216 colors that displayed consistently across all major browsers.':'网页安全色源自互联网早期，是一组 216 种在主要浏览器中显示一致的标准调色板。','HTML Color Names':'HTML 颜色名称','Color Names':'颜色名称','Modern browsers support 140 named colors, which are listed below. Use them in your HTML and CSS by name, Hex color code, RGB or HSL value.':'现代浏览器支持 140 个命名颜色，下面列出了这些颜色。你可以在 HTML 和 CSS 中按名称、Hex 色号、RGB 或 HSL 值使用它们。','Color Names':'颜色名称','Color Codes / HTML Color Names':'颜色代码 / HTML 颜色名称','Modern browsers support 140 named colors, which are listed below. Use them in your HTML and CSS by name, Hex color code, RGB or HSL value.':'现代浏览器支持 140 个命名颜色，下面列出了这些颜色。你可以在 HTML 和 CSS 中按名称、Hex 色号、RGB 或 HSL 值使用它们。','Browse our list of HTML color names and find the Hex, RGB, and HSL values for common CSS color keywords.':'浏览 HTML 颜色名称列表，查找常用 CSS 颜色关键字的 Hex、RGB 和 HSL 值。','Minecraft Color Codes':'Minecraft 颜色代码','Color Codes / Minecraft Color Codes':'颜色代码 / Minecraft 颜色代码','Browse our list of Minecraft color codes and formatting codes for chat, MOTD text, signs, books, and server messages.':'浏览 Minecraft 聊天、MOTD 文本、告示牌、书本和服务器消息可用的颜色代码与格式代码。','List of Minecraft Color Codes':'Minecraft 颜色代码列表','Minecraft color codes let you change the color of chat messages, server text, signs, books, and other supported text. Use the section sign code with the color or formatting character shown in the table.':'Minecraft 颜色代码可以改变聊天消息、服务器文本、告示牌、书本和其他支持文本的颜色。请使用表格中的分节符代码和颜色或格式字符。','Click any code or Hex value to copy it.':'点击任意代码或 Hex 值即可复制。','Bukkit Color Codes':'Bukkit 颜色代码','Color Codes / Bukkit Color Codes':'颜色代码 / Bukkit 颜色代码','Browse our list of Bukkit color codes for plugin configuration files, ranks, menus, chat text, and server messages.':'浏览 Bukkit 插件配置、等级、菜单、聊天文本和服务器消息可用的颜色代码。','List of Bukkit Color Codes':'Bukkit 颜色代码列表','Bukkit color codes use the ampersand character followed by a color or formatting code. They are commonly used in server plugins, configuration files, ranks, menus, and chat text.':'Bukkit 颜色代码使用 & 符号加颜色或格式代码，常用于服务器插件、配置文件、等级、菜单和聊天文本。','Roblox Color Codes':'Roblox 颜色代码','Color Codes / Roblox Color Codes':'颜色代码 / Roblox 颜色代码','Browse our list of Roblox Color Codes or BrickColor Codes--the preset named colors used in developing games for the online platform Roblox.':'浏览 Roblox Color Codes 或 BrickColor Codes，这些是 Roblox 平台游戏开发中使用的预设命名颜色。','List of Roblox Color Codes':'Roblox 颜色代码列表','Roblox color codes are commonly shared as BrickColor names, numbers, and RGB values. Use the table to find familiar Roblox colors for parts, UI, themes, and design references.':'Roblox 颜色代码通常以 BrickColor 名称、编号和 RGB 值共享。使用表格查找适合部件、UI、主题和设计参考的 Roblox 颜色。','Click any value to copy it.':'点击任意值即可复制。','Converted Color':'转换后的颜色','Color 3':'颜色 3','Color 4':'颜色 4','Color 5':'颜色 5','Color 6':'颜色 6','Color 7':'颜色 7','Color 8':'颜色 8','Color 9':'颜色 9','Color 10':'颜色 10','Color 11':'颜色 11','Color 12':'颜色 12'},
